TransLoc,is,a,transportation,information,system,for,mass,transportation,riders,Features,of,TransLoc,include,real,time,display,of,transit,system,detailed,maps,view,of,where,busses,are,in,real,time,and,estimated,arrival,times,The,TransLoc,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,TransLoc,with,other,applications,and,to,create,new,applications,Some,example,API,methods,include,retrieving,transportation,agency,information,accessing,information,based,on,geolocation,and,managing,user,accounts